      "message": "[🟡 Suggestion] Line 356: The new locking around getPonderateLoss() only protects pondLoss_, but setNewPacketLoss() is still called outside mutex_ and mutates packetLoss_ without synchronization while other code may read it under the same session mutex. Keep the packet-loss state update in the same critical section or make packetLoss_ atomic. Suggested fix:\\n```suggestion\\n    float pondLoss;\\n    {\\n        std::lock_guard lock(mutex_);\\n        pondLoss \u003d getPonderateLoss(rtcpi-\u003epacketLoss);\\n        setNewPacketLoss(static_cast\u003cunsigned int\u003e(pondLoss));\\n    }\\n```",
